Title: Dendrogram Seriation: Ordering for Visualisation
Description: Re-arranges a dendrogram to optimize visualisation-based cost functions.
    The methods implemented here are described in "Advances in Dendrogram Seriation for Application 
    to Visualization", Journal of Computational and Graphical Statistics (2015) D. Earle and C.B. Hurley  <doi:10.1080/10618600.2013.874295>.
